div.div: This is the story of an orphan, L Shu. He is not any regular orphan, but a metahuman experiencing the changes in himself, his country and the world during the dawn of the magical era. Watch as L Shu embarks on a journey to hone his peculiar abilities together with his sister, the adorable and charismatic L Xiaoyu. Along the way, theyll encounter supernatural events, obstacles and even the most powerful people in their country. How will L Shu make the best of his abilities and oust his never-ending list of rivals and opponents? (Source: Webnovel) Note: Includes 29 extra chapters.

This is a world where anyone can have the chance to become a god. Choose the path of thunder, one can become a Thunder God. Choose the path of the mountain, one can become a Mountain God. After becoming a god, you can create your own divine kingdom. Lai Cang transmigrated into this world with no money and no talent to take on the path to becoming a god. But after a lucky accident, he found himself with a divine kingdom of his own, despite never completing the path to godhood!

(Source: Tencent, translated)
